ticked-off trannies with knives is a 2010 rape and revenge exploitation film . the film follows a trio of trans women friends who exact revenge on the men who brutally assault them and murder two of their friends . the film is split into five chapters , one of which is a missing reel . ticked-off trannies engendered controversy when it was programmed at the 2010 tribeca film festival . the gay & lesbian alliance against defamation condemned the film for what it called a negative portrayal of transgender people .